<h1>Feedback</h1>

<br/>

<%= simple_form_for(@feedback) do |f| %>
  <%= f.input :name %>
  <%= f.input :email %>
  <%= f.input :content, input_html: { rows: long_entry_row_num } %>
  <%= f.button :submit, 'Submit' %>
<% end %>

<br/>
I'd love to hear your your thoughts on what features you'd most like added next, as well as aspects about the current site you think can be improved. <strong>I promise I will respond to any feedback you share with me!</strong>
<br/>
<br/>
(P.S., if you've also got nice things to say, my primate brain would really really appreciate if you share that with me :D It'll make me more motivated to work on this, and by corollary more likely to add features you'd like!)